('king_lear_act3_scene4',102,'S. Withold footed thrice the old; He met the night-mare, and her nine-fold; Bid her alight, And her troth plight, And, aroint thee, witch, aroint thee!'),
('king_lear_act3_scene4',111,'But mice and rats, and such small deer, Have been Tom’s food for seven long year.'),
